{"tid":1519443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 80多日抗爭後 政府終於跪低聽民意 開出第一個民主大門!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:10:54.000Z","uid":82312,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad55cd3b388342993deae8ee7159af38c61407b","tid":1519443,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"4月開始嘅遊行 直到100萬人200萬人嘅和平遊行<br />\n直到後來兩個幾月嘅暴力抗爭<br />\n政府今日終於要跪低 聽民意<br />\n雖然唔係回應5大訴求<br />\n但中央同政府都表示<br />\n行唔行緊急法會聽取大家意見<br />\n視符聽日示威者情況<br />\n<br />\n我地連登仔一定要爭取最好表現<br />\n實現我地行緊急法嘅終極目標<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推行緊急法</span></span><br />\n如果聽日唔成功 就好可能比到錯覺中央同官員<br />\n覺得香港人都唔想要民主<br />\n咁普選一定冇望<br />\n聽日大家識得做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攬炒</span>"},{"pid":"ed965887bda8ade22c7b5c01256536229bd05f4c","tid":1519443,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=794dc872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-